title: FSX - SceneryTech - World Landclass
description:
Set of SceneryTech Landclass Addons for FSX including:


North America

South America

Europe

Asia

Indo Pacific


Note: Africa is not released yet


Not my own release but found.


Installation:


1. Just install them
2. Have fun

... yea its that easy!


Note: This will work with UTX. Please read the FAQ and manual of UTX for further information on how to set up the scenery library correctly.
